### Component 4: Backend — Fix getApprovers() (UPDATE)

#### [MODIFY] [users.service.ts](file:///d:/iDesk/apps/backend/src/modules/users/users.service.ts)

**Saat ini** (line 493-499):
```typescript
async getApprovers(): Promise<User[]> {
  return this.userRepo.find({
    where: { isActive: true },  // ← Terlalu luas! Semua user aktif
    order: { fullName: 'ASC' },
    relations: ['department'],
  });
}
```

**Perbaikan:**
```typescript
async getApprovers(): Promise<User[]> {
  return this.userRepo.find({
    where: [
      { role: UserRole.MANAGER, isActive: true },
      { role: UserRole.ADMIN, isActive: true },
    ],
    order: { fullName: 'ASC' },
    relations: ['department'],
  });
}
```

Ini memastikan ManagerSelector hanya menampilkan user dengan role MANAGER atau ADMIN.

